name: 'Leonardo da Vinci on the return to Florence' (VS VIEW-MASTER series)
description: This work is part of the "Vs View-Master" series begun in 2013. 'Vs View-Master' series project explores via the neglected spaces or interstices that exist between images and words, the meaning, influence and place occupied by emotion, stereotypes of these same representations, and our imagination. Full collection here: https://www.lenieblue.com/vs-view-master
